oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall and soldiers from the 40th School Squadron
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall sitting in the grass. He is with other United States Army Air Corps soldiers from the 40th School Squadron at the Kelly Air Force Base (now known as Kelly Field Annex), located in San Antonio, Texas. Kinsall is located in the first row, on the far right.
